high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the left side of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward to face the trash can on the floor.
Cut the apple in the trash can into three pieces.
Place the knife in the trash can next to the apple.
Pick up the piece of apple in the trash can.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the shelves.
Place the piece of apple in the pot on the second shelf from the bottom.
Pick up the pot with a piece of apple in it.
Turn around and walk forward and turn right to face the fridge.
Place the pot with a piece of apple in it in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To put a piece of apple in a pot as well as move it to the fridge.

high_descs: Go to the sink
Pick up the knife from the drying knife
Go to the green bin
Cut the green apple in the bin
Put the knife in the bin
Take an apple slice from the bin
Go to the shelves
Place the apple slice in a pot
Take the pot
Go to the fridge
Put the pot in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a cut green apple slice in the fridge

high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter, left of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right, move to the bin next to the refrigerator.
Slice the apple in the bin.
Put the knife in the bin.
Pick up a section of apple from the bin.
Turn right, move to in front of the shelf.
Put the apple section in the pot.
Pick up the pot from the shelf.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the pot in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot containing sliced apple into the refrigerator.
